&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;assembling-the-device&#34;&gt;Assembling the device&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There are two ways of assembling the device:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;using surface-mount soldering method&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;soldering on PCB&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The first version of adapter was made for testing, so I used surface-mount method:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/post/making-and-adapter-to-connect-3.5mm-sound-jack-line-output-to-microphone-input/IMG_20240610_151218_642.jpg&#34;
