&lt;h3 id=&#34;final-look&#34;&gt;Final look&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Finally I decided not to make any custom case for it (as adapter has really tiny PCB) and used termosetting to cover the PCB. The total length of cable is 1.5 meters, which I think is fine for most of the cases.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/post/making-and-adapter-to-connect-3.5mm-sound-jack-line-output-to-microphone-input/IMG_20240610_180318_597.jpg&#34;
